article_title: MNsure technology barriers are barriers to coverage

article_metadata.description: Tuesday was the start of open enrollment under the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act, using new state health insurance marketplaces. In Minnesota — and across the country — technology issues impeded enrollees from learning about plan options, and from signing up for coverage.

og.description: In Minnesota and across the country, technology issues have prevented enrollees from signing up for coverage.
